        <abstract> 
<p>Requests HM’s article in the <hi rend="italic">Witness</hi> [24 Feb 1855; see HM, "On the late severe frost", <hi rend="italic">Proc. R. Phys. Soc. Edinburgh</hi> 1 (1854–8): 10–14], on the effects of frost on shells. CD expresses admiration for the two works by HM he has read.</p> 
